{"tid":2446084,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK〈How You Like That〉MV 破八億　刷新韓國女團最快紀錄！","createTime":"2021-03-14T07:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T10:31:54.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d2302739217632c392b8c5b65fdc502969bbaa9","tid":2446084,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_74a6c370296b6c5a50410c31918a088c/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-14/134248-899997.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_74a6c370296b6c5a50410c31918a088c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-14%2F134248-899997.png&h=79c431a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨天 BLACKPINK 的 &quot;How You Like That&rdquo; 表演影片觀看數才剛破六億次，正式 MV 又緊接著抵達新的里程碑！<br />\n<br />\n在 13 日晚間約 9 點時，BLACKPINK 的 &quot;How You Like That&rdquo; 官方 MV 觀看次數突破了八億次，成為國女團史上最快獲得這項成績的 MV。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_36615b120c78b408e1e18329932a121e/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-14/134248-899998.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_36615b120c78b408e1e18329932a121e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-14%2F134248-899998.jpeg&h=046cc447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;How You Like That&rdquo; 是去年為 BLACKPINK 首張正規專輯〈THE ALBUM〉揭開序幕的歌曲，延續 &ldquo;DDU-DU DDU-DU&rdquo;、&ldquo;Kill This Love&rdquo; 雄壯的氛圍再加上更多亮點，在發行後成功橫掃海內外排行榜，華麗的 MV 也大獲好評。<br />\n<br />\n包括 &ldquo;How You Like That&rdquo; 在內，BLACKPINK 已經有 &ldquo;DDU-DU DDU-DU&rdquo;、&ldquo;Kill This Love&rdquo;⋯⋯等 5 支觀看次數逾八億次的作品，與防彈少年團並列為坐擁最多破八億 MV 的韓國歌手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment）"},{"pid":"e4fee3f31c637eb9a627f32619038eb4fbfb823d","tid":2446084,"uid":255310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />👍🏻"},{"pid":"59769723f33725124f53d26ceee9a8ab84067a08","tid"